                <td width="525" class="alignTop"><p align="left"><span class="style3">Thank you for  taking the time to visit Canada's oldest cruise agency, The Cruise People Ltd.</span><br>
                      <em> </em></p>
                  <table width="80%" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
