                  <p align="left">                    Our motto simply enforces  that we are not only the leading experts in the cruise industry for the last thirty  years but a family owned company that strives to maintain it.&nbsp; We specialize in cruises, yet many clients  use our other services for all their requirements when booked in conjunction  with their sea holiday.&nbsp; Everything from  airline tickets, travel insurance, coach tours, package holidays in Canada, the  United States and abroad and hotel bookings.&nbsp;</p>
                  <p align="left"> Visit our <strong class="navLink"><a href="travel-destinations.html" class="lightBlueLink">Destinations</a></strong> section for some exceptional getaways or  our<a href="freighter-voyages.html" class="lightBlueLink"> <strong>Passenger Freighte</strong></a><strong><a href="freighter-voyages.html" class="lightBlueLink">r</a></strong> section for a true sea farer adventure!</p>
                  <p>Contact our helpful and  friendly <strong><a href="about_us.html" class="lightBlueLink">Cruise Specialists</a></strong> for expert advise and assistance:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>we specialize  in all cruise and passenger freighter lines </li>
                    <li>tours and  group tour travel</li>
                    <li>individual,  incentive and business travel</li>
                    <li>Cruise&nbsp; Lines International Association (CLIA)  affiliate</li>
                    <li>all the  professional services you would expect from Canada's oldest travel experts</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p>We at The Cruise People  look forward to serving you and encourage you to <strong><a href="contact_us.html" class="lightBlueLink">contact us</a> </strong>for a unique  and memorable experience.</p>
                  <p>Happy Voyage!</p>
